benchmark_config.jira_title: Implement/Test API: GET /1.0/kb/admin/queues - Get queues entries

covered: Valid Request: Multiple positive retrieval scenarios with default and filtered responses
Empty Response: Tests for no data and filters excluding data
Query Parameters: Extensive testing of filters (accountId, queueName, serviceName, date ranges, flags, extra parameters, partial input, combined filters)
Authorization: Tests for unauthorized access (invalid token) and 401 scenarios
gaps: Pagination: No tests cover pagination handling for large datasets
Rate Limiting: No tests cover how the system handles multiple requests in a short time
Caching Behavior: No scenarios testing caching behavior (ETag, Cache-Control headers)
recommendations: Add tests for pagination to ensure proper handling of large datasets
Include rate-limiting/throttling tests to verify behavior under high request volume
Add tests for caching headers and behavior (ETag, Cache-Control) and verify caching-related responses
